name: Onshape
0:
”Alexa ask Onshape for the version”
”Alexa ask Onshape what is the status”
”Alexa ask Onshape help on Sketching”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: on shape
des:
This Alexa skill can retrieve information about Onshape's CAD service. You can ask about the version/build number or what the status of the service is in the event there is a service disruption.(CAD modeling service, Forum, Support system, Billing etc).

In addition, you can also ask the skill what's new and it will read the change log for the current version or have it retrieve help articles based on various keyword searches.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
